          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\colon  B\to  C]]></fr:tex> be <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000W.xml" title="inverse" addr="forest://erct/erct-000W" type="local">invertible</fr:link> maps. Then the composite <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\circ  f\colon  A\to  C]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000W.xml" title="inverse" addr="forest://erct/erct-000W" type="local">invertible</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
